{"tid":2013574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"放寬左限聚令先黎本地確診，識玩！六旬婦確診報稱三個月無外遊","createTime":"2020-05-12T11:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T03:55:23.000Z","uid":213877,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"553922d6315c157ac3065b7b7dc5f4b0fdd9332b","tid":2013574,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-29_q1Tb5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-1-29_q1Tb5_1200x0.png&h=10baafa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》從三個獨立消息得悉，本港在經歷 23 天沒有本地個案後，再次「斷纜」。消息指，瑪嘉烈醫院接獲一宗武漢肺炎確診個案，病人是一名 66 歲婦人，居於梨木樹村，報稱近三個月沒有離開香港。消息又指，經衞生署覆檢後，病人已證實為確診。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名女病人居於梨木樹村，昨日因發燒到荃灣伍若瑜普通科門診求醫，今日樣本顯示初步確診，將轉送瑪嘉烈醫院接受隔離治療。消息指，病人已發燒 3 天，亦有喉嚨痛及輕微咳嗽等上呼吸道病徵。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士則指，該病人的樣本經衞生署覆檢後，證實為確診。<br />\n<br />\n若消息屬實，本地沒有本地個案的紀錄將「斷纜」。之前衞生署曾指，若 28 日沒有本地個案，可視為本地傳播鏈斷截，各限制社交措施亦可逐步放寬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-消息-23-日本地零感染-斷纜-六旬婦初步確診報稱三個月無外遊/?fbclid=IwAR1FRMg64_H2kp1k-FvRDPOWnujrFbsCMdDPxcTkrRqkV6MCs_pnMCC5hrk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-23-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%B6%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E6%96%B7%E7%BA%9C-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%84%A1%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1FRMg64_H2kp1k-FvRDPOWnujrFbsCMdDPxcTkrRqkV6MCs_pnMCC5hrk&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=341e5c64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-23-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%B6%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E6%96%B7%E7%BA%9C-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A9%A6%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%89%