,"uid":267801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"永續限聚令。"},{"pid":"84617ea2b55e3aa38a55111f3cd39c4f5a37276f","tid":2013574,"uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507593-20200209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507593-20200209.htm&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=1331229d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507593-20200209.htm&h=732005e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507593-20200209.htm</a><br />\n有市民在梨木樹邨的商場對開空地聚集，警員到場後截查多名市民。（港台記者攝）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">醫管局將位於葵涌的伍若瑜夫人普通科門診診所，列為新型肺炎疫情下的指定診所之一</span>。有診所附近居民不滿有關安排，晚上在梨木樹邨聚集，大批軍裝警員晚上約10時到場，截查多名市民。<br />\n<br />\n有市民在梨木樹邨的商場對開空地聚集，收集居民簽名，反對將伍若瑜夫人普通科門診診所列為指定診所，部份人一度在邨內遊走，並高叫口號。警員到場後截查多名市民，又要求他們舉高雙手。<br />\n<br />\n部份警員在附近巡查後離去，亦有警員一度進入商場內巡邏。<br />\n-----------------------------分隔線-----------------------------<br />\n據了解，該名女病人居於梨木樹村，昨日因發燒到荃灣<span style=\"color: red;\">伍若瑜普通科門診求醫</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf9bb1058858b0c3e54119789f0ca8f292474dd","tid":2013574,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84617ea2b55e3aa38a55111f3cd39c4f5a37276f","tid":2013574,"uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507593-20200209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507593-20200209.htm&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=1331229d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embe